; Test auto transaction with amount_expr producing long integer result
; Exercises lines 1049-1050 of xact.cc

= Expenses:Food
    (Assets:Budget)    (1)

2024/01/01 Grocery
    Expenses:Food    $25.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg Assets:Budget
24-Jan-01 Grocery               (Assets:Budget)              $25.00       $25.00
end test
